lead_paragraph: Russell Westbrook had 32 points, 12 rebounds and took over late to lead the Oklahoma City Thunder to a 103-97 victory over the Philadelphia 76ers on Wednesday night.

headline.print_headline: Westbrook, Thunder Spoil Embiid's Debut for 76ers
